{"tid":468749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菜檔姐偷$530斷正，檔主初頭要求賠18萬，但最後放人了事！","createTime":"2017-11-14T16:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T12:27:32.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3dac1e93fada53319d6cf3e761a4f875c94650","tid":468749,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"今日網上流傳一段影片，一名菜檔老闆疑在店內，捉拿一名負責睇檔的女下屬偷錢，並拍片放到網上公審。只見老闆要女店員翻開手袋，拿出一大堆10元硬幣，店主與另一男子從旁數錢，懷疑當日店員偷了總值530港元的10元硬幣：「我落咗汗，（菜檔收回來的）10蚊點咗藍色筆（記認）喺度。」只見店員並無反抗，無奈站在一旁。<span style=\"color: red;\">姓葉店主其後回覆東網指，因店員年紀老邁，不欲報警拘捕她，因此希望拍片，以示懲戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/photo/bkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171114232458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171114232458&h=311253d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/bkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171114%2Fbkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001.html&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9dWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=3b72e50e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/bkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1265786430114911/permalink/2182677618425783/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1265786430114911%2Fpermalink%2F2182677618425783%2F&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9dWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=da600979\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1265786430114911/permalink/2182677618425783/</a></div>"},{"pid":"d0834467544b5690c8eb35b548fdb90079d0d501","tid":468749,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"從該段片長6分半鐘的影片所見，菜檔男店主找人舉機拍攝，與疑偷錢的女店員對質。男店主拿着點了記認的10元硬幣，表示早已由店內CCTV拍攝到其偷錢過程，並非插贓嫁禍。男店主稱：「你自己解釋，發生咗咩事，點解會有530蚊大餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」女店員其後當場承認，當日偷了530港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。店主因此估計，該店員半年內每日偷500元硬幣及500元紙幣，總數18萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，要店員賠償「畀錢贖身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，亦懷疑菜檔前1個月虧蝕10萬元，與其偷錢有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"f3053f3877e80f4e320248d3c17a22f4f757641d","tid":468749,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:07:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6e708a9c9249e099f00cd7c235fd271ce2d9851","tid":468749,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"有網民不值女店員行為，認為人贓並獲，店主可直接報警坐監留案底。但有網民怒斥店主做法，該店主如此對質，有可能誤墮法網：「你自己都識講我今日捉到你係咁咪賠番530蚊畀你，香港法律係要講證據，你嗰半年都捉唔到係你弱雞啫，個老細隨時畀人告多條恐嚇勒索，監守自盜係最多罰5000，個老細仲以為自己好型！」"},{"pid":"f403ba61421eba1768f1c7d67e592d812c40bbd5","tid":468749,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"「依家冇報警只為放左佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」該個位於黃大仙竹園街市菜檔的店主葉先生，回覆東網表示，片段拍攝於約2星期前。未有報警追究除因怕麻煩，亦因該女伙計已60多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，事後亦未有叫她賠錢就放她走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「啲伙記知道件事後，一時之間大家都唔知點處理，始終相處半年有感情，有啲伙計仲流眼淚喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」"},{"pid":"70c69b224464c7f99f01d593153e535b9ee55072","tid":468749,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"店主續指，他經營的菜果檔共有6至7名員工，涉事阿姐負責睇菜檔，至今已工作半年，是登報紙以日薪大概700元聘請。直至近月，發現10元硬幣的數量大減，認為情況有異，經翻查閉路電視後發現有員工偷錢。發生此事後，他並不打算放上網，只是發送了給一些同行，以示警惕。後來有人擅自將片段放了上網，「我都唔想搞到咁大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」不過，店主直指，女店員一直未有悔意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  。"},{"pid":"14ca5489a7377c7c05d4926a73b71f4c33f3efed","tid":468749,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/photo/bkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001_06b.jpg?20171114232458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20171114232458&h=ecee3100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">店員一般都把用作找續的硬幣放在膠兜內。</span></div>"},{"pid":"17a03b218110829450cd2e75c1befe4760f738cd","tid":468749,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/photo/bkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001_05b.jpg?20171114232458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20171114232458&h=b4f09828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">涉事菜檔位於黃大仙竹園街市。</span></div>"},{"pid":"73329a57990ee3e1f79f9579bcb1afe7782fc21f","tid":468749,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:13:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171114/photo/bkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001_04b.jpg?20171114232458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171114194054001-1114_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20171114232458&h=35d5fd0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">店主葉先生現身解畫，指事後未有叫她賠錢就放她走。</span></div>"},{"pid":"7b4ef7190139d5d431344f3da21bf52523d3538b","tid":468749,"uid":37525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"條片入面阿叔光頭<br />\n上報條友咁多頭髮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773782d44ce42bdc32918ad8a3c71ebb5c556414","tid":468749,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條片入面阿叔光頭<br />\n上報條友咁多頭髮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍檔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc817fa018a227db121d6bed7902dc68510100d","tid":468749,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"七百蚊日薪 高過好多fg 都唔知足？"},{"pid":"eba036f507f7c641bbb2e19000a0c6b09c5236b1","tid":468749,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:28:20.000Z","msg":"兩個齊齊坐咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d101c82a1f22690536a3cb4b30abd66ed3f6263","tid":468749,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"個店主有D似鍾鎮濤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054948b36817a1a312cf17e63ce342695c78fd95","tid":468749,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"做得好 不過最後太慈祥喇"},{"pid":"8bbbdab398c8228055e11b28a5059c49a1f3982f","tid":468749,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>